//   OK (Automatic expungement for misdemeanors — 2025)
//   DC (Revised sealing law — February 2025)
//   CT (Automatic erasure expanded — 2023)
//   MN (Manual + automatic expungement — 2025)
//   MT (Automatic sealing of some records — 2024)
